      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      346.18,
      526.35,
      360.35
    ],
    "text": "1. The Judge's failure to adequately analyze critical evidence and",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      367.78,
      526.38,
      381.95
    ],
    "text": "testimonies raises substantial questions about the Judicial assessment of",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      389.38,
      439.49,
      403.55
    ],
    "text": "the presented evidence in the course of the judicial process.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      423.1,
      526.39,
      437.27
    ],
    "text": "2. The failure to apply the correct legal standards and to recognize",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      444.7,
      526.34,
      458.87
    ],
    "text": "discrepancies in evidence caused the Judgment to be bad in Law and in",
