    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      543.24,
      420.89,
      557.41
    ],
    "text": "thereby the Judgment and the conviction is bad in Law.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      576.84,
      526.3,
      591.01
    ],
    "text": "4. Learned High Court Judge failed to apply judicial decision considering",
