      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      729.99,
      526.36,
      744.16
    ],
    "text": "a friend of her brother. On the day in question, she had gone to the boutique to",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      751.58,
      526.57,
      765.76
    ],
    "text": "purchase soap, and while on her way, she had encountered the appellant at",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      779.14,
      327.38,
      805.78
    ],
